{"tid":983569,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英大學涉歧視華學生 警告勿cheating加註中文「舞弊」","createTime":"2019-01-16T05:34:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-16T09:31:28.000Z","uid":150685,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a59d41c15a20394ffd2ae091dedb1d71054630","tid":983569,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:34:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190116/large/1547603281_1ef4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190116%2Flarge%2F1547603281_1ef4.jpg&h=48508955&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文電郵附加一個敏感詞的中文字解釋，算不算歧視？英國利物浦大學（University of Liverpool）近日向外國留學生發送了一封電郵，提醒他們在考試期間作弊的嚴重後果，卻因在英文字cheating後特別用中文「舞弊」作註解，令來自中國的學生十分不滿。<br />\n<br />\n有中國留學生向校方表達不滿，認為有關做法具爭議。校方隨後回覆指，這是因為「學校的中國學生通常不熟悉cheating這一英文單詞，所以我們提供了它的中文繙譯『舞弊』」。<br />\n<br />\n這個解釋令在該校就讀的中國留學生更加不滿，他們認為校方不該在發給所有國際學生的英文郵件中，單獨使用中文解釋敏感詞彙，此舉明顯涉嫌歧視，會讓人覺得來自中國的學生都有作弊的可能。<br />\n<br />\n校方後來又發聲明，就事件所引發的誤解致歉之餘，還表示之前發出有關考試的提醒，並非針對某特定學生群體。不過，校方仍堅持，因為以往出現過中國學生對英文不理解，加上中文繙譯只是為了更好地傳達考試規範。<br />\n<br />\n內地網友對今次事件反應兩極，有網友認為，「應該自省自律，反思中國留學生到底是否存在作弊較為嚴重的情況。感覺涉嫌歧視，還是談不上。」但亦有人指，「哪個留學生會連『Cheating』是甚麼意思都不知道？未免太針對中國人了」、「我看是中國學生成績太好你們懷疑是『舞弊』來的，分明是嫉妒！」 ​<br />\n<br />\n《中國日報》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190116/59148299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59148299&d=SX%2BUoBDMe9%2BAxfAiwDzPbOargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=96b59b17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190116%2F59148299&h=387ac3b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190116/59148299</a>"},{"pid":"4ffb26c80b72d5b9fa905254e3b7f879f078784b","tid":983569,"uid":107364,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b03ad386c77cf72033995c4d638136acc11bf860","tid":983569,"uid":121911,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"去外國讀書唔識cheating點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個解釋撚鳩人"},{"pid":"e19cb386ddf2b6505d58317ef8d9b91621e6da9f","tid":983569,"uid":17765,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:37:12.000Z","msg":"支那賤種其實唔使寫中文提<br />\n直接踢出校 沒收visa 掟返支那"},{"pid":"3d4ab73e962215f120f1fb53c79cd9deb7eadf88","tid":983569,"uid":130575,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"b03ad386c77cf72033995c4d638136acc11bf860","tid":983569,"uid":121911,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"去外國讀書唔識cheating點解？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個解釋撚鳩人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:38:36.000Z","msg":"班友靠cheat先過到外國，唔識唔出奇，況且係蝗國呢d可能唔算cheating，有文化差異<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f4cda1339b4636b653380e6837fe8213f48340","tid":983569,"uid":209908,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:44:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">「我看是中國學生成績太好你們懷疑是『舞弊』來的，分明是嫉妒！」</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5R3XAhB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5R3XAhB.jpg&h=4fac4e1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n班支那狗睇到自己咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"178d2ef659e34ebc74847e64910a06d18166187b","tid":983569,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0f4cda1339b4636b653380e6837fe8213f48340","tid":983569,"uid":209908,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-16T05:44:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"c